  "text": "Culture. Human GBM cell lines (U251-MG and T98) were purchased from Cell Bank of Institute of Biochemistry and Cell Biology, Shanghai Institutes for Biological Sciences. Briefly, cells were cultured with Dulbecco's Modified Eagle's medium (DMEM) supplemented with 10% fetal bovine serum in an incubator with 95% O 2 and 5% CO 2 as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
